#thfc Spurs spokesman on Hugo Lloris&rsquo; drink driving charge: &ldquo;The Club takes matters such as this extremely seriously and it will be dealt with internally.&rdquo;<br />
<br />
Lloris: &ldquo;I wish to apologise wholeheartedly to my family, the Club, my teammates, the manager and all of the supporters. Drink driving is completely unacceptable, I take full responsibility for my actions and it is not the example I wish to set.&rdquo;
